          <p class="lead msg">Aaj ka din tujhe utni roshni laut ke de jitni tu doosron ko deti hai. Khush reh, hasti reh — aur thoda mere liye bhi muskura dena. 💜</p>
          <p class="bright">It's your day —<br>but it makes mine too. 🥹<br>so please, enjoy &amp; smile 💖</p>
